---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
import { people } from '@content/_data'
---

<Layout title="About Resplice">
	<div class="bg-white pt-48 pb-24 sm:py-36">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Mission</h2>
				<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
					Solving Identity by changing the way we connect and share.
				</p>
			</div>
			<dl
				class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 text-base leading-7 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3"
			>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Connecting the World, Your Way</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						At Resplice, we believe that connecting with others should always be your choice. We're
						on a mission to redefine personal connections, putting you in control of your data and
						your interactions.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
						Empowering Personal Connections with Transparency and Control
					</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						In a world where privacy is paramount, Resplice stands out as a platform that values
						your data as much as you do. We envision a future where connecting with friends, family,
						colleagues, and even businesses is effortless and secure. With Resplice, you can create
						meaningful connections without compromising your privacy.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Your Privacy, Your Rules</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						Resplice is more than just a connection platform; it's a reflection of your preferences.
						We offer a central profile where you can manage emails, social media accounts, phone
						numbers, addresses, and shared credentials. But here's the twist - you decide who sees
						what. With selective sharing, you have the power to customize your profile for different
						connections.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Effortless Connections</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						We want to make connecting with other people, businesses, & services as easy as
						possible. Marrying ease of use and security is key to our mission of creating a
						world-class connection experience.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Community and Trust</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						Resplice values the trust of its user community and seeks to foster a sense of community
						among its users. Building trust through transparency, security, and user-focused
						services is a core value.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div>
					<dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Inclusivity</dt>
					<dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">
						Identity is a fundamental human right. Resplice values inclusivity, ensuring that its
						platform is accessible to a diverse range of users, regardless of their backgrounds,
						abilities, or preferences.
					</dd>
				</div>
			</dl>
		</div>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 mt-24">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
					Meet our leadership
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
					We're two founders who are passionate and ultra-focused on solving the identity problem
					and creating a platform that empowers people to connect and share on their terms.
				</p>
			</div>
			<ul
				role="list"
				class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-20 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:max-w-4xl lg:gap-x-8 xl:max-w-none"
			>
				{
					people.map((person) => (
						<li class="flex flex-col gap-6 xl:flex-row">
							<Image
								class="aspect-[4/5] w-52 flex-none rounded-2xl object-cover"
								src={person.image}
								alt="Resplice Founder"
							/>
							<div class="flex-auto">
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">
									{person.name}
								</h3>
								<p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">{person.role}</p>
								<p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">{person.bio}</p>
							</div>
						</li>
					))
				}
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
